tqSGw">Trần Quốc Tuấn - 陳國俊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Minh-Khi%C3%AAm/author-P_O0C8eAMSSE0VWCvRAM-w">Đặng Minh Khiêm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BA%ADt/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-t%C3%ACnh-bi%E1%BB%83u/poem-AGKUOTf4MNBoRtTrY2zw2A">Trần tình biểu - 陳情表</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BA%ADt/author-2WZpsdSFEWvTQerf8uTifQ">Lý Mật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-T%C3%B4-Hi%E1%BA%BFn-Th%C3%A0nh/poem-ntePeM4NDdtMaNEF9Lu2SA">Vịnh Tô Hiến Thành - 詠蘇憲成</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Tri%E1%BB%87t/X%C3%ADch-B%C3%ADch-ho%C3%A0i-c%E1%BB%95/poem-eMPV8BV_zdmTnEOU9HV9xA">Xích Bích hoài cổ - 赤壁懷古</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Tri%E1%BB%87t/author-fXc_gqkrGBbO64QEuTFarQ">Tô Triệt</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
